data.description: Welcome to Murray Hill! This classic bungalow is ready for a new owner. The home has large rooms and an back porch with a Master Forge outdoor kitchen. Enjoy Florida evenings on the back porch living area. The kitchen and bathroom are updated along with the electric and plumbing. Come see this adorable bungalow today and start living the Murray Hill lifestyle.
